            "file": "core/agents/manim_code_generator.py",
            "action": "MODIFY",
            "detail": "Add to LLM prompt: 'When creating RightAngle, ensure the two lines are perpendicular, not parallel or collinear. Verify coordinates before using RightAngle.'"
          }
        ]
      },
      "verification": "Retry manim_codegen for section 7, check generated code for RightAngle usage, run manim_render."
